notesStmt.note: This workshop discussion at a student conference on the topic of universities in capital cities deals with the relationship between being a student and being a citizen. S1 and S2 are the chairs, with S2 dominating. The main concepts under consideration are citizenship and different kinds of community. The participants are student representatives from different countries/universities and have only known each other for one day. Loud background noises can frequently be heard on the recording. The participants discuss matters enthusiastically and occasionally joke with each other.

equipment.p: Portable minidisc recorder with electret condenser stereo microphone
